title: Keep It Simple Juicing Healthy Snacks Made Easy with Jason Vale
description:
Juicing doesn't need to be difficult, you just need to Keep it Simple! Jason's ultimate guide to quick and simple juicing made incredibly easy. This new DVD is distinctly different from the 'Keeping It Simple' book and contains sections from 'Simply Gorgeous Smoothies' to a great 'Kid's Stuff' section. A must if you're getting into juicing or want some great new tips to make juicing simple, quick and easy.
